com.foursquare.geo.shapes.indexing

Class CellLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foursquare.geo.shapes.indexing.CellLocation

  • public class CellLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines a location in the index, relative to a CellLocationReference The index represents the path to a node in a Quadtree-like structure, but is suitable for representing a quadtree-like structure in a Map, using CellLocation as a key.
